column5: What's going on here I just logged in an the first page is full of topics asking how to use a computer. Must me alot of guys quenching there thirst and not fishing like me. Lol I'm finally comin home from work tomorrow an will be off for at least a few months. Il be on a mission for some perch and some pike finally. Here's to hoping the ice is hard and the fish are hungry!
I think you might need some computer help yourself...
